          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#ffffff' fontname='Tableau Bold' fontsize='18'>YouTube Trending Video Analytics Dashboard</run>
            <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#ffffff' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Negative-sentiment titles drive nearly 2x the average views of neutral content, despite making up only 15% of trending videos.</run>
          </formatted-text>
          <zone-style>
            <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
            <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
